text: America's Next Top Model, Cycle 11 is the eleventh season of America's Next Top Model. This cycle includes 14 contestants. The winner was 19-year-old McKey Sullivan. ==Contestants== (In alphabetical order) * Brittany "ShaRaun" Brown * Nikeysha Clarke * Marjorie Conrad * Clark Gimler * Lauren Brie Harding * Elina Ivanova * Isis King * Joslyn Pennywell * Samantha Potter * Brittany Rubalcaba * Sheena Satana * Brittany "McKey" Sullivan * Analeigh Tipton * Hannah White ==Prizes== * A modeling contract with Elite Model Management * A spread in Seventeen Magazines * A $100,000 contract with CoverGirl ==Episodes== 1\. casting episode 2\. *Best: Marjorie Conrad *Worst: Nikeysha Clarke & ShaRaun Brown *Eliminated: ShaRaun Brown 3\. *Best: Lauren Brie Harding *Worst: Isis King & Nikeysha Clarke *Eliminated: Nikeysha Clarke 4\. *Best: Elina Ivanova *Worst: Brittany Rubalcaba & Analeigh Tipton *Eliminated: Brittany Rubalcaba 5\. *Eliminated Outside Of Judging Panel: Hannah White *Best: Clark Gimler *Worst: Samantha Potter & Isis King *Eliminated: Isis King 6\. *Best: Samantha Potter *Worst: Joslyn Pennywell & Clark Gimler *Eliminated: Clark Gimler 7\. *Best: Marjorie Conrad *Worst: Sheena Satana & Lauren Brie Harding *Eliminated: Lauren Brie Harding 8\. *Best: Analeigh Tipton *Worst: Joslyn Pennywell & Elina Ivanova *Eliminated: Joslyn Pennywell 9\. *Best: McKey Sullivan *Worst: Sheena Satana & Elina Ivanova *Eliminated: Sheena Satana 10\. *Best: Samantha Potter *Worst: Elina Ivanova & Marjorie Conrad *Eliminated: Elina Ivanova 11\. *Best: Analeigh Tipton *Worst: Marjorie Conrad & Samantha Potter *Eliminated: Marjorie Conrad 12\. *Best: McKey Sullivan *Worst: Samantha Potter & Analeigh Tipton *Eliminated: Analeigh Tipton *Final Two: Samantha Potter & McKey Sullivan *Winner: McKey Sullivan Category:America's Next Top Model
